 t Cohen Tentet\, Matt Wilson's Honey and Salt\, and the Mark Morris Dance
  Group\, and is a member of the electro-acoustic new music trumpet ensemb
 le Fifth Bridge. She has been commissioned to compose works for a diverse
  range of groups\, including the legendary British brass institution Grim
 ethorpe Colliery Band\, modern classical string and brass ensembles\, and
  pieces for solo trumpet and fixed media. Noordhuis has released four alb
 ums of original compositions featuring her quintet and duo projects throu
