  (Music Tectonics)    - Timirah James (Artist\, AI Music researcher)    -
 &#160\; Andy West (IU Jacobs School of Music)    The summit provides an o
 pportunity to wrestle with questions about authorship\, ownership\, envir
 onmental impact\, cultural disruption\, business transformation\, and the
