 ony\, Orquesta Juvenil Universitaria Eduardo Mata\, American Composers Or
 chestra\, Texas Festival Orchestra at Round Top\, and returns to the Gros
 sman Ensemble\, Sichuan Symphony\, and Thailand Philharmonic. Passionate 
