 n Piano Performance with Gilbert Kalish at Stony Brook University.<br /><
 br /><strong>Tichina Vaughn</strong> is associate professor of music in v
 oice at the Indiana University Jacobs School of Music. A Grammy Award-win
 ning American mezzo-soprano\, celebrated for her "superb\, rich singing" 
